Beastbox swaggered out of the consol room. He cluched at his head
tightly. "Beastbox, not feel so good." and he fell to the ground, as his
eyes became dim.

Motormaster looked at Beastbox, and scowled. "Whoever hurts a
Decepticon, AWNSERS TO ME." He announced, as he transformed into his
truck mode, and drove towards Slaughter, shaking the halls of the ship.
